description	"Dark Jedi Cultist Healer:
A Dark Jedi who specialises in Healing and Support, they carry Sonic Detonators instead of Lightsabers.

^2Weaponry:
- 3 Sonic Detonators

^5Force Powers:
- Jump  (2)
- Push  (2)
- Pull  (2)
- Sense (2)
- Lightning (1)
- Drain (1)
- Team Heal (1)
- Team Energize (1)

^8Attributes:
- BP Free Jumps
- Resistant to Melee Attacks
- View Ally Stats
- Bunny Hop (1)
- Slow Faller
- Mind Trick Immunity
- Cortosis (1)
- 1 Extra Life

^3Abilities:
- Health Dispenser [Hold Use to Heal Allies]
- Ammo Dispenser"